So I can’t wait to try stuff out. 💙💙💙

Basic info:
Name:
Reign Suzuki (Suzuki...
body:
First bnha oc design I’ve made out of several others I need to make. :)

Basic info:

Name:

Reign Suzuki (Suzuki Reign)

Age:

15

Course:

Support Department (1st year)

Quirk:

Quirkless

///

Reign is a very smart, straightforward person with a very realistic view set on the world. She’s been creating small inventions ever since she could hold objects and has always had an interest in creating new, useful things that could benefit to others.

It takes a while to “befriend” Reign, mostly due to the fact she usually isolates herself away to work on a new invention rather have face to face communication with another person. She doesn’t have friends, only people she can tolerate to have around her, but don’t expect that to happen so easily.

Both of Reign’s parents have very strong and powerful quirks, thus a good part of herj childhood consisted of people either astonished she’s quirkless and pity her, or laugh and ridicule her for not being strong like her parents. It’s because of this that she learned to ignore the majority of others opinions and thoughts (especially about her). She uses all her past encounters with those people to drive herself to create only the best inventions and support items for others to use.

Reign, as anti-social as she may be, is highly curious and fascinated about quirks and how they work from person to person, and conducts organized, controlled experiments to those who are willing to be her test subject. When she’s not doing that, most of the time she will either be continuing her work on a regular support item, or designing specific ones for students who need them for their hero costume.

☆

Oof if you took the time to read all that bless you.
